{"id":37168,"date":"2024-02-18T15:58:11","date_gmt":"2022-08-18T10:28:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=37168"},"modified":"2024-09-28T19:43:32","modified_gmt":"2024-09-28T14:13:32","slug":"interior-design-cost-in-mumbai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/interior-design-cost-in-mumbai\/","title":{"rendered":"Decoded: Interior Design Costs In Mumbai For Every Home Type"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A complete guide on interior design costs in Mumbai for every type of home as per the design experts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mumbai is India\u2019s cultural melting pot. Thousands of people come here from different parts of the country to fulfil their dreams and become one with the city&#8217;s culture. The Arabian Sea, bustling trains, lip-smacking street food, breezy beaches and posh nightlife \u2014 encompass the financial capital of India. The one disadvantage of life in Mumbai is the cramped up apartments and sky-rocketing real estate prices. But, when thinking of dream homes, the last thing we can think of is compromise. So, if the humongous quotes of interior design costs per square foot in Mumbai make you doubt your decision of going for your dream <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interiors<\/a>, we have the perfect solution for you. This detailed guide on interior design costs in Mumbai will give you an idea of what to expect and what budget you need to make your house a well-designed and functional haven of your choice. Read along to know more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Home interior design depends on endless factors, be it the size of your home, the furniture pieces you want, the materials and finishes you choose and also the design style you prefer. But to give you an idea, we have divided the quotes of interior design costs in Mumbai into two verticals \u2014 the \u2018must-have\u2019 and the \u2018good-to-have\u2019 elements. When you are opting for a basic budget, you can expect the must-have elements in your house. But, if you want to design your home with the \u2018good-to-have\u2019 elements, expect a higher budget. So, before going deep into the interior design costs in Mumbai, let&#8217;s explore the difference between the must-haves and the good-to-have list.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>For the must-have list, you can expect:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Kitchen with base cabinets and wall unit<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A basic TV unit in the living room<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A small shoe rack&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wardrobe with loft overhead<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Double bed in the bedroom<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For finishes, you can get a combination of high gloss, textured and matte laminates<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>In the good-to-have list, you can expect:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Kitchen with extra storage units like drawers and loft units with glass shutters<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>TV unit with wall panelling for the living room<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Double bed with fabric headboard and side table with dresser<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A space-saving vanity unit to dress up in the comfort of your bedroom<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Modular wardrobe with overhead loft designed in high-end finishes like Abety laminates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A foyer unit in the entryway<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>French classic trims on the walls of your home<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For finishes, you can expect a combination of Italian laminated, high gloss and matte laminate for a premium look.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"941\" height=\"2223\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide.jpg\" alt=\"Guide on selecting the ideal interior design partner for your home\" class=\"wp-image-59413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide.jpg 941w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-127x300.jpg 127w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-433x1024.jpg 433w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-768x1814.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-650x1536.jpg 650w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-867x2048.jpg 867w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/28194146\/interior-design-partner-selection-guide-150x354.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know the factors determining the large share of the cost of home interiors in Mumbai, let&#8217;s tell you how the cost varies as per the size of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1 BHK Interior Design Cost In Mumbai<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Home interiors of a 1 BHK that include the basic elements and finishes will cost you anything between <strong>INR 4 lakhs to 4.5 lakhs<\/strong>. And if you are looking for a premium finish with additional storage and decor like mentioned in the good-to-have list, expect the cost to shoot up to around <strong>INR 6 lakhs to 6.5 lakhs<\/strong>. The cost of the interiors also depends on the quality of paints, lights, fixtures and style of your home interiors. For example, a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/minimalist-home-design-ideas\/\">minimalist home interior<\/a> with basic furniture and decor will cost you much less than an eclectic interior with high-end modular furniture and finishings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154928\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"1 bhk interior design cost in Mumbai range starts from INR 4 lakhs\" class=\"wp-image-37170\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154928\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154928\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154928\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154928\/1-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A guide on interior design cost for a 1 BHK in Mumbai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2 BHK Flat Interior Design Cost In Mumbai<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For the home interiors of a 2 BHK in Mumbai, the cost can range from <strong>INR 5.5 lakhs and go up to 6 lakhs<\/strong> for the basic quality. For premium finishes and additional interior design elements; as mentioned earlier, the cost can range from INR 8 lakhs and go up to 9 lakhs. Again, the cost depends a lot on the materials, finishes, furniture and style of your home interiors. The cost also varies depending upon the seating area of your home and the utility of your second bedroom. If you want to use it as a kid&#8217;s room with modern home interiors, the price will shoot up compared to using it as a basic utility room or a guest room with minimal home interiors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154935\/2-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"2 bhk flat interior design cost in Mumbai depends on materials, finishes, furniture and style\" class=\"wp-image-37171\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154935\/2-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154935\/2-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154935\/2-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154935\/2-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The cost of interior design for a 2 BHK flat in Mumbai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3 BHK Interior Design Cost In Mumbai<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are among the luckiest lot to own a 3 BHK home in Mumbai and are looking for home interiors, the cost depends on the square feet and how you want to use your extra room. For example, the cost of the interiors will come down a good extent if you are using the extra room as a den area or a small library with minimal furniture. Whereas, the cost may shoot up if you are planning to add a murphy bed and modular study unit with high laminates for your kid. But to give you a fair idea, the cost can range from INR <strong>9 lakhs to 9.5 lakhs<\/strong> for the basic materials and finishes. And for the best home interior design in Mumbai with high-end materials and finishes, the cost can range approximately between INR 8 lakhs to 9 lakhs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154941\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"3 bhk interior design cost in Mumbai depends on the square feet\" class=\"wp-image-37172\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154941\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154941\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154941\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154941\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">How much do 3 BHK interiors cost in Mumbai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4 BHK Interior Cost In Mumbai<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a 4 BHK home in Mumbai is quite a dream come true. So, if you have a 4 BHK home in Mumbai, you should definitely go for a beautiful home interior to amplify your space. The cost of personalised home interiors will range somewhere around <strong>INR 12 lakhs to 18 lakhs<\/strong> depending on your choice and preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154947\/4-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"4 bhk interior design cost in Mumbai range around INR 12 lakhs to 18 lakhs\" class=\"wp-image-37173\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154947\/4-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154947\/4-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154947\/4-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18154947\/4-bhk-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">How much do 4 BHK interiors cost in Mumbai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cost of designing a Villa in Mumbai<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The cost of home interiors for a villa in Mumbai depends on the number of rooms and the square area of your home. But you can expect the range to be something above INR 15 lakhs and the price rises higher as you increase the requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18155001\/villa-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg\" alt=\"Villa interior design costs in Mumbai range above INR 15 lakhs\" class=\"wp-image-37175\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18155001\/villa-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18155001\/villa-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18155001\/villa-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/18155001\/villa-interior-design-cost-in-mumbai-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Cost of home interiors of a villa in Mumbai<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is all about home interior design costs in Mumbai. Please do note that these quotations are just for reference purposes. Every home is different, so the exact quotations can only be given after we know the details of your home, your preferences and the feasibility. If you want to get a detailed quotation, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">book a free consultation<\/a> with our best <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-mumbai\/\">interior designers in Mumbai<\/a>, and they will help you with personalised designs that suit your budget and your requirements. You can also visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/experience-centre\/\">our Experience Centres<\/a> to check out the latest interior design concepts and talk to our designers directly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/w